Rock Paper Scissors Lizard Spock

Game Rules:
0. Say hello! (Welcome player)
1. Display Rules
2. Let user select game mode (Number of players or AI)
3. display options to player
4. pick a gesture from list
    5. second player / AI picks
6. compare gestures
    7. same gestures - no winner
    8. Declare winner of round
9. Keep playing rounds until we can "declare winner"
10. Declare winner!!

player -
    human
    AI


